{"tid":1416904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解成日都有人話打狗係等於場運動失焦","createTime":"2019-08-05T15:44:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T20:04:33.000Z","uid":258797,"like":63,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f2364ce26bcd5cd31dfdd0391c3914e9ae09ef6a","tid":1416904,"uid":258797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:44:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span><span style=\"color: red;\"></span>政府匿係警察後面<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span> <br />\n唔先解決警察可以點?<br />\n同你攻城一樣 你唔解決企係城牆上面既弓手 你點撚樣攻入去?<br />\n<br />\n唔係話啲咩 但係發過咁多次夢 最後變成打狗唔係無原因 因為政府會先派狗出嚟打擊示威者<br />\n69開始有邊次唔係咁<br />\n<br />\n唔好成日當勇武係白痴啦 <br />\n由始至終都係針對五大訴求"},{"pid":"5c792da1a9893c33430e9d84eacd6e623ed8cb99","tid":1416904,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:44:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4c1e0ef031af1e80336e72d2812d928daa8f7236","tid":1416904,"uid":165198,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:45:44.000Z","msg":"唔好中林鄭既計，家陣講緊我地誤傷途人同主動分化唔同立場既人<br />\n你地好勇冇問題，睇實前線既手足唔好亂對街坊"},{"pid":"6e3115610497263ae5045d06a472a7bc98aedea6","tid":1416904,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:46:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">請全世界入黎！！究竟我地係咪要港獨？目標要一致！！<br />\n</span><br />\n如果唔係爭取港獨，請立即澄清<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1416445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1416445</a>"},{"pid":"2ac98702adedbfcf724dc513f62a180b73f7a902","tid":1416904,"uid":258797,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:46:45.000Z","msg":"我就真係唔明 <br />\n仲有班人話玩火太過份 <br />\n係咪無上過去前面一分鐘食一粒催淚彈?<br />\n癲架屌你<br />\n何況火都未撚燒狗<br />\n都唔知有咩好嘈"},{"pid":"220c9cbe0d4f89c46dc1c22138cd47d064bc003b","tid":1416904,"uid":258797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4c1e0ef031af1e80336e72d2812d928daa8f7236","tid":1416904,"uid":165198,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:45:44.000Z","msg":"唔好中林鄭